cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.SE

The paper proposes a method for detecting concept drift in multivariate log files, which involves machine learning and data analysis techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as they also deal with data analysis and modeling. Additionally, cs.DB (Databases) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) are also possible categories as they involve managing and analyzing large datasets.
